          "solution": "[식 설정]\n$x=29$로 치환하여 다항식 $P(x) = x^3 - 5x^2 - 13x - 7$의 인수를 먼저 찾는다.\n[전개]\n1. 인수분해:\n$P(-1) = (-1)^3 - 5(-1)^2 - 13(-1) - 7 = -1-5+13-7 = 0$이므로 $(x+1)$을 인수로 갖는다.\n조립제법을 이용하면:\n$P(x) = (x+1)(x^2-6x-7) = (x+1)(x+1)(x-7) = (x+1)^2(x-7)$\n\n2. 자연수 $N$의 값 계산 및 소인수분해:\n$x=29$를 대입하면,\n$N = (29+1)^2(29-7) = 30^2 \\times 22$\n$N = (2 \\times 3 \\times 5)^2 \\times (2 \\times 11)$\n$N = 2^2 \\times 3^2 \\times 5^2 \\times 2 \\times 11$\n$N = 2^3 \\times 3^2 \\times 5^2 \\times 11^1$\n[조건 적용]\n양의 약수의 개수는 각 소인수의 지수에 1을 더해 모두 곱하여 구한다.\n약수의 개수 $= (3+1) \\times (2+1) \\times (2+1) \\times (1+1)$\n$= 4 \\times 3 \\times 3 \\times 2 = 72$\n\n[시각 자료: 소인수분해 구조도]\n<svg viewBox=\\\"0 0 240 100\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" style=\\\"display:block;margin:10px auto;\\\"><rect x=\\\"10\\\" y=\\\"30\\\" width=\\\"40\\\" height=\\\"40\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"black\\\" /><text x=\\\"20\\\" y=\\\"55\\\" font-size=\\\"14\\\">2³</text><text x=\\\"55\\\" y=\\\"55\\\" font-size=\\\"14\\\">×</text><rect x=\\\"70\\\" y=\\\"30\\\" width=\\\"40\\\" height=\\\"40\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"black\\\" /><text x=\\\"80\\\" y=\\\"55\\\" font-size=\\\"14\\\">3²</text><text x=\\\"115\\\" y=\\\"55\\\" font-size=\\\"14\\\">×</text><rect x=\\\"130\\\" y=\\\"30\\\" width=\\\"40\\\" height=\\\"40\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"black\\\" /><text x=\\\"140\\\" y=\\\"55\\\" font-size=\\\"14\\\">5²</text><text x=\\\"175\\\" y=\\\"55\\\" font-size=\\\"14\\\">×</text><rect x=\\\"190\\\" y=\\\"30\\\" width=\\\"40\\\" height=\\\"40\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"black\\\" /><text x=\\\"195\\\" y=\\\"55\\\" font-size=\\\"14\\\">11¹</text></svg>\n\n[결론]\n따라서 자연수 $N$의 양의 약수의 개수는 72이다.\n∴ 정답은 ④",
          "unitKey": "H1-01",
          "_sourceTitle": "original/high/h1/1mid/25_금당고_1학기_중간_고1_기출",
